  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a trial to demonstrate the safety and effectiveness of the Freedom SOLO heart valve
      when used to replace a diseased or dysfunctional aortic valve or aortic valve prosthesis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
